<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Verification OTP</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f7f9;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #007bff 0%, #0056b3 100%);
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .welcome-text {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .otp-container {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border: 2px dashed #007bff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }

        .otp-code {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #007bff;
            letter-spacing: 8px;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .expiry-notice {
            color: #888;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .footer {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #aaa;
            font-size: 12px;
        }

        .divider {
            height: 1px;
            background: #eee;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Account Verification</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p class="welcome-text">Hello <strong>
                    <%= name %>
                </strong>,</p>
            <p>Thank you for joining us! To complete your registration and verify your account, please use the following
                one-time password (OTP):</p>

            <div class="otp-container">
                <h2 class="otp-code">
                    <%= otp %>
                </h2>
            </div>

            <p>Enter this code on the verification page to get started.</p>

            <p class="expiry-notice">This code is valid for <strong>2 minutes</strong>. If you did not request this,
                please ignore this email.</p>

            <div class="divider"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Startup Template. All rights reserved.<br>
                If you have any questions, contact our support team.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>